Summary: Bright light, 5x as fast as a commercial jet and a little higher in elevation travelling across the sky above the clouds.
divs: Sighting Detailswas outside the house smoking and looking at the stars when I seen an object that looked like a bright star that was a little bit higher than a commercial jet flys and moving about 5times as fast.. it was following a long stretch of clouds and went acrossed the sky until it was out of sight. no noise and was waaay faster than anything ive ever seen flying in the sky.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Canyon Lake and Lake Elsi
